# Universal noise (stack-agnostic base). A language stack overlay appends its own
# build/tooling ignores (e.g. .venv/, __pycache__/) on top of this.

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.local

# Private per-clone agent notes — the update-safe home for project-specific guidance (AGENTS.md
# itself re-renders on `copier update`). The `.md` suffix escapes `*.local`, so pin it explicitly.
# Create it yourself when you have notes to keep; it is never committed and Copier never touches it.
AGENTS.local.md

# Local environment + secrets (never commit; commit a .env.example instead)
.env
.envrc

# Scratch / local-only working space
.scratch/

# Local-only session handoffs (never shipped). The structure-lint skips git-ignored paths,
# so frontmatter-less handoffs under here do not trip the docs gate.
docs/sessions/
